<createdBy>bosarie</createdBy>
<createdTime>2023-10-13 09:26:12 UTC</createdTime>
<commentInRDBMS><![CDATA[A Term debt security is a Debt security that has a fixed maturity date and is not redeemable before that date.

This can be a term debt security that runs until its maturity date and is not redeemable before that date, or it can be a callable debt security that, when certain conditions are met, can be redeemed before its maturity date.]]></commentInRDBMS>
